text: Tewelde Estifanos (born 2 November 1981) is an Eritrean long distance runner who specialises in the marathon. He competed in the men's marathon event at the 2016 Summer Olympics where he finished in 60th place with a time of 2:19:12. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Eritrean male long-distance runners Category:Eritrean male marathon runners Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic athletes of Eritrea
